</div>
<div class="qa-block">
<h2>What kind of expertise is necessary to initiate AEO?</h2>
<p>AEO requires senior-level strategic advisory, technical implementation expertise in structured data, and content strategists experienced in conversational funnel design.</p>
</div>
</section>
<section class="tradeoffs">
<h2>Tradeoffs</h2>
